	measure 'Fixed price - Actual percentage - estimate of closed projects' = ```
			
			/* ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
			Purpose
			- Return the actual "Estimate" (Estimate activity) amount for ongoing
			  fixed-price projects, ensuring that:
			    • The Budgeted ticket Amount is not blank or zero
			    • The State is not "Closed"
